10... Nc7 $146 {Interesting novelty, even though I don't see anything wrong
with the normal} (10... Qc7) 11. Nc3 Bg7 12. Re1 ({There is no advantage for
White either after} 12. Rd1 Qc8 13. Bf4 O-O 14. Rac1 Bxc4 15. Qxc4 Qe6 $11)
12... O-O 13. Bf4 Nd4 $1 {The right moment to simplify} 14. Nxd4 Qxd4 15. Bxe6
